snippet.textDisplay:
This version from Atif is very soothing and calming. His voice is unique. 

But the original one still hits the soul. 
Still gives the goosebumps. 
Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan was magical.
Though music in the original one is distracting...
It didn't age well.
The one without music and with highnotes is incredible.

I am glad this version has less distracting music.
It may pass the test of time longer than previous.

But still wanna add love to Nisrat Fateh Ali Khan and the person or persons who wrote it.
This piece they delivered was soulfull.
And still wins heart.

We know music isn't good. 

May Allah help us in walking in the right path. And help us understand things better and help us act on the right deeds. Aameen.
